# ── GitHub Models ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This agent uses the GitHub Models inference endpoint instead of
# calling OpenAI directly.  All you need is a GitHub Personal Access
# Token (classic or fine-grained — no special scopes required).
#
# Create one at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
#
# Model usage is billed through your GitHub Copilot subscription.
# See the README for full pricing details.
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...

# Optional overrides
# ESS_MODEL=gpt-4.1
# ESS_MAX_TURNS=25

# ── MCP servers (configure the ones you need) ──────────────────────
# Each server needs its own URL + Bearer token because they hit
# different SaaS APIs with separate OAuth scopes.
#
# For dev: acquire tokens manually (az cli, Postman, platform CLI)
# For prod: use a client-credentials or OBO token provider — the
#           only thing that changes is how you populate these vars.

# ESS_WORKDAY_MCP_URL=https://your-host.azurecontainerapps.io/workday/mcp
# ESS_WORKDAY_TOKEN=eyJ0eXAi...

# ESS_SERVICENOW_MCP_URL=https://your-host.azurecontainerapps.io/servicenow/mcp
# ESS_SERVICENOW_TOKEN=eyJ0eXAi...

# ESS_SALESFORCE_MCP_URL=https://your-host.azurecontainerapps.io/salesforce/mcp
# ESS_SALESFORCE_TOKEN=eyJ0eXAi...

# ESS_JIRA_MCP_URL=https://your-host.azurecontainerapps.io/jira/mcp
# ESS_JIRA_TOKEN=eyJ0eXAi...
